<HEADLINE>
<P>
DIGEST / LOCAL NEWS IN BRIEF: GALLEGLY NAMES LIMON AS FIELD REPRESENTATIVE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
U.S. Rep. Elton Gallegly (R-Simi Valley) has announced that Al Limon will serve 
as his new field representative beginning today. 
</P>
<P>
Limon will provide a link between Gallegly and his constituents in the 21st 
Congressional District. Limon worked in real estate last year after serving as 
a field representative for Rep. Robert J. Lagomarsino (R-Ojai). 
</P>
</TEXT>
