<HEADLINE>
<P>
GREENHOUSE EFFECT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I have read many articles about the Greenhouse effect. It frightens me that 
despite constant warning by scientists, no concerted effort is being made by 
the nations of the world to prevent it. 
</P>
<P>
When we gamble on the validity of the Greenhouse effect, it's like playing 
Russian roulette. The Greenhouse gun is aimed at our world. Is the barrel 
loaded or empty? If nothing is done, we'll soon find out. 
</P>
<P>
BING LEE 
</P>
<P>
Laguna Niguel 
</P>
