</P>
<P>
17. County-Harbor UCLA Medical Center, Torrance 
</P>
<P>
18. County-Martin Luther King/Drew Medical Center, Los Angeles 
</P>
<P>
22. St. Mary Medical Center, Long Beach 
</P>
<P>
23. Memorial Medical Center of Long Beach 
</P>
<P>
