seclusion to plead not guilty to eight federal drug and perjury charges, then 
returned to a substance-abuse treatment center. Meanwhile, members of the 
crime-fighting Guardian Angels, above, picketed outside the court demanding 
Barry's resignation. Associated Press 
</P>
