<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORNING REPORT: PEOPLEWATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By CLAUDIA PUIG, Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bush Cancels Paramount Visit: President Bush, who had been scheduled to take a 
tour of Paramount Studios this morning, instead will visit the new North County 
Correctional Facility in the hills below Castaic, the White House said. A 
spokesman said that the studio visit was scrubbed for logistical reasons and 
that Bush would still be able to talk to studio executives at a breakfast 
speech Friday before the Academy of Television Arts &amp; Sciences. CLAUDIA 
PUIG 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
