<P>
QUAKE FISH: Oscar, Corona del Mar High's famed earthquake prognosticating fish, 
wasn't around to forecast Wednesday's temblor (A1). . . . "Oscar bit the dust 
-- he took a deep-six on us about a month ago," said Principal Tom Jacobson. . 
. . The one-eyed South American red oscar died of "simple old age," he said. 
