Photo, Above, Vicky Bates of Newport Beach gets an opinion from her husband, 
Steve, on an outfit. LACY ATKINS / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Below, the 
7,500-square-foot store is the latest addition in Henry Segerstrom's grand plan 
to upgrade the caliber of his tenant mix in South Coast Plaza. 
</P>
