<P>
The hearing for track and field coach Chuck DeBus set for today has been 
rescheduled, according to The Athletics Congress, the national governing body 
of track and field. TAC announced that the hearing, which has been rescheduled 
several times, would be continued at the request of DeBus' attorney. DeBus, 
formerly a coach at UCLA and Cal State Northridge, has been under investigation 
by TAC for allegedly providing banned substances to athletes. 
</P>
