<TEXT>
<P>
President Bush has found a rich vein of joke material: the divorce battle 
between Donald and Ivana Trump. 
</P>
<P>
On a fund-raiser for a Republican candidate in a Staten Island congressional 
election, Bush said his visit to New York had put him in the midst of "one of 
the greatest contests of 1990," a battle with "a lot at stake, a lot of money 
